CustomField.description: Tree node type. Can be one of o 'NodeType_Root' - the top most root node that can have static children only as defined in configuration o NodeType_Object - an object is displayed as tree node o NodeType_GroupByRoot - group nodes inside this using group by field o NodeType_Query - nodes inside this node comes from query result
CustomField.inlineHelpText: o NodeType_Root - node that can have static children only o NodeType_Object - an object is displayed as tree node o NodeType_GroupByRoot - group nodes inside this using group by field o NodeType_Query - nodes inside this node comes from query result
CustomField.label: Type
